&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Martock and South Petherton Surgeries &lt;/strong&gt;require a part time Receptionist/Administrator on a &lt;strong&gt;10 - 12 month fixed term basis&lt;/strong&gt;. The post available will be working 24 hours per week, Mondays and Thursdays 8.30-6.30 and Fridays 1.30-6.30.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You should have excellent communication skills and have the ability to work as part of a team. You should be IT literate and be able to work accurately and prioritise your workload.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Previous experience of reception work in a medical environment is desirable but not essential.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please open the attached Job description for a comprehensive overview of the role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For more information contact Lisa Tabner, Practice Manager on 01460 247519 or email lisa.tabner@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
